I&#39;ve been thinking about this myself, IMO, the key to solving the problem is
to
1. Tie resource links i.e. &lt;link rel=&quot;&lt;operation&gt;&quot; (hypermedia) to a known
set, an ontology of operations, perhaps; or a finite set of operations
2. having the client handle different media types as &quot;plugins&quot; ... just the
way we a &quot;web&quot; browsers work.

IMHO, ATOM pub services are an easier subset of RESTful services to have a
universal client for

